      "content": "You should focus on covering four main pillars: Appearance, Communication, Cultural Awareness, and Professional Conduct. Appearance should detail appropriate dress codes for various international settings, while Communication needs to cover verbal and written clarity across different languages and formalities. Cultural Awareness is crucial for navigating local customs, and Professional Conduct covers timeliness, respect, and handling business interactions ethically. These pillars will give your readers a comprehensive framework for looking and acting polished globally.",
